{"tid":2027560,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國間諜衛星系統下月建成  全球半數國家已使用","createTime":"2020-05-21T12:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T12:26:30.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a25928a61366bd013bb0613aa4403172aa2a95fe","tid":2027560,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"北斗全球衛星系統下月建成 全球半數國家已使用<br />\n21.05.2020 20:10<br />\n<br />\n中國北斗衛星導航系統工程總設計師楊長風透露，北斗3號衛星定位系統最後一枚組網衛星，將在6月發射，屆時北斗全球星座的布局將完成。<br />\n<br />\n楊長風在政協委員通道接受傳媒訪問時說，北斗全球衛星系統的建設用兩年時間，被稱為中國速度，中國智能手機已有超過7成提供北斗服務，目前世界上已有半數以上的國家使用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289154&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289154%26csid%3D261_341&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoVy8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=46b099b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289154&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"d20281fdd680bb5dfc195041469d20168956b474","tid":2027560,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:24:39.000Z","msg":"稱霸地球 指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc325cdc45edfd3554300784e47028bc42faa00a","tid":2027560,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:26:30.000Z","msg":"支那好努力咁製造太空垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}